The paper also discusses the capacity achieving input distribution, which is related to source coding (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper deals with the issue of additive noise, which is a topic in control theory (cs.SY). Finally, the paper mentions the limit of arbitrarily many uniform quantization levels, which is related to machine learning and signal processing (cs.MM).
